  #################################################
  # Previously (June 2024), we considered that in 2050, all power plants must have 0 emissions
  # To reflect that, we forced all emitting plants to burn only RNG
  # A Do If loop included all plants receiving a decision and that do not burn 100% RNG in 2050, minus BTF plants.
  # CCS were exempted because they were near 0 emissions and their status was more complex if they start burning RNG.
  # TD (July 2024): we enabled offsets in 2050, therefore there was no need to force a 100% RNG fuel mix
  
  WriteDisk(db,"EGInput/UnFlFrMax",UnFlFrMax)
